Ferragamo to Sell Shares at 8 Euros to 10.50 Euros Each in Public Offering

-- B y   E l i s a   M a r t i n u z z i
-- 
2011-06-10T18:53:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-10/ferragamo-to-sell-shares-at-8-euros-to-10-50-euros-each-in-public-offering.html
Salvatore Ferragamo SpA said it will
offer shares in an initial public offering at 8 euros to 10.50
euros apiece, the company said in an emailed statement today.  The shares will be on offer from June 13 through June 23,
the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Elisa Martinuzzi at 
 emartinuzzi@bloomberg.net  